Events Collection
- Event Year: NUMBER (YYYY)
- Event Code: NUMBER (YYYYMMDD)
- Event Name: STRING
- Google Drive: STRING (Google Drive Link)
- Access List: Array[Member ID] (Managed by Cloud Functions, Firestore Rules)
- Event Overall In-Charge: STRING (Managed by Cloud Functions)
- Event Assistant In-Charge: STRING (Managed by Cloud Functions)
- Event Members: Participation Collection

Participation Collection
- Event Code: NUMBER (YYYYMMDD)
- Member ID: STRING
- Full Name: STRING
- Role: STRING (XXX)
- VIA Hours: NUMBER (X HOURS)